<li id="cite_note-auto3-35"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-auto3_35-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-auto3_35-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-auto3_35-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFCarlos_BC2021" class="citation web cs1">Carlos BC, Juan (9 December 2021). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211209173612/https://www.fairobserver.com/region/middle_east_north_africa/juan-carlos-bc-syria-news-bashar-al-assad-syrian-president-arab-world-news-83492/">"The Assad Family Has Been Shaping Syria for 50 Years"</a>. <i>Fair Observer</i>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.fairobserver.com/region/middle_east_north_africa/juan-carlos-bc-syria-news-bashar-al-assad-syrian-president-arab-world-news-83492/">the original</a> on 9 December 2021.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Fair+Observer&amp;rft.atitle=The+Assad+Family+Has+Been+Shaping+Syria+for+50+Years&amp;rft.date=2021-12-09&amp;rft.aulast=Carlos+BC&amp;rft.aufirst=Juan&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fairobserver.com%2Fregion%2Fmiddle_east_north_africa%2Fjuan-carlos-bc-syria-news-bashar-al-assad-syrian-president-arab-world-news-83492%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAlawites" class="Z3988"></span></span>
